{"source_url": "https://stanleymuseum.uiowa.edu/event/35608/0", "title": "School's Out at the Stanley | Wobbly Eggs", "description": "Make your very own collection of weighted easter eggs that won't fall over. Use them to play, decorate, or hide around the house! Space is limited; please reserve your spot at https://uiowa.doubleknot.com/event/schools-out-at-the-stanley-wobbly-eggs/3114202 Please arrive in time for children to settle in and begin the project at 2 p.m. School's Out at the Stanley is offered on days when Iowa City Community Schools District has no classes. Art projects are developed with school-aged children in mind...", "venue_name": "Stanley Museum of Art", "location_text": "Stanley Museum of Art", "city": "Iowa City", "state": "IA", "activity_type": "class", "age_min": null, "age_max": null, "drop_in": false, "registration_required": true, "start_at": "2026-04-03T14:00:00", "end_at": "2026-04-03T15:30:00", "timezone": "America/Chicago", "free_verification_status": "uncertain", "is_free": null}
{"source_url": "https://stanleymuseum.uiowa.edu/event/33175/0", "title": "Night at the Museum: Student Showcase", "description": "Once a month, the Stanley hosts events designed to introduce the museum to University of Iowa students through engaging and creative activities. Nights at the Museum events occur on Thursday nights when the museum is open late. These events are planned and developed with the assistance of the Campus Engagement Coordinator, a student employee who works with museum staff to engage student audiences. Information about past Nights at the Museum can be found here . Attending student events also...", "venue_name": "Stanley Museum of Art", "location_text": "Stanley Museum of Art", "city": "Iowa City", "state": "IA", "activity_type": "activity", "age_min": null, "age_max": null, "drop_in": false, "registration_required": false, "start_at": "2026-04-09T17:00:00", "end_at": "2026-04-09T19:00:00", "timezone": "America/Chicago", "free_verification_status": "uncertain", "is_free": null}
